data.description: Practically new (2021 build) 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the Centennial North neighborhood and award winning Vicksburg School District. The main floor features a beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dark birch cabinets, snack bar, white subway tile backsplash, wood vinyl flooring and a spacious pantry. The kitchen and dining area open directly into the great room with vaulted ceilings, which give an open and spacious feel to the home. Also on the main floor, you will find a primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom. In the lower level of the home, you have plenty of additional living space with 2 more large bedrooms, another full bathroom, laundry room and rec room. The deck off the living room is a great spot for grilling out and entertaining.
